    <arm_group_label>Cohort 5</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>This is a sub-study testing the effect of real output applied under two adhesive strips on the skin after 8 hours.
There is one visit:
Two adhesive strips (standard adhesive strip and Experimental adhesive strip)are applied on the peristomal skin and allowed to sit for 8hours before being removed.</description>
  </arm_group>
